org.openscience.smsd.algorithm.vflib

Class VF2MCS

  • java.lang.Object
    • org.openscience.smsd.algorithm.vflib.BaseMCS
      • org.openscience.smsd.algorithm.vflib.VF2MCS
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    IResults

    public final class VF2MCS
extends BaseMCS
implements IResults
    This class should be used to find MCS between source graph and target graph. First the algorithm runs VF lib VF2MCS and reports MCS between run source and target graphs. Then these solutions are extended using McGregor McGregor algorithm where ever required.
    Author:
    Syed Asad Rahman

      • getAllAtomMapping

        public List<AtomAtomMapping> getAllAtomMapping()
        Returns all plausible mappings between query and target molecules. Each map in the list has atom-atom equivalence of the mappings between query and target molecule i.e. map.getKey() for the query and map.getValue() for the target molecule
